{"prompt": "Generate a website for a community non-profit. The website should be playful and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Community Connect</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0f8ff; /* Alice Blue for a light, airy feel */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #4682b4; /* Steel Blue - the brand color */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        h2, h3 {\n            color: #4682b4; /* Steel Blue */\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .section img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #4682b4; /* Steel Blue */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 25px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #5a9bd1; /* Lighter blue for hover */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #4682b4; /* Steel Blue */\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        .highlight {\n            color: #4682b4; /* Steel Blue */\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Community Connect</h1>\n        <p>Building a Brighter Future Together!</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Welcome to Our Community!</h2>\n            <p>We are a passionate non-profit organization dedicated to <span class=\"highlight\">strengthening our neighborhood</span> through fun events, essential services, and fostering genuine connections.</p>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/600x300/ADD8E6/FFFFFF?text=Community+Event\" alt=\"Happy people at a community event\">\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2>What We Do</h2>\n            <p>From organizing local <span class=\"highlight\">park clean-ups</span> and hosting <span class=\"highlight\">skill-sharing workshops</span> to providing resources for those in need, we're here to make a difference.</p>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/600x300/B0E0E6/FFFFFF?text=Helping+Hands\" alt=\"Volunteers working together\">\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Get Involved</h2>\n            <p>Your participation matters! Whether you have time to volunteer, a skill to share, or simply want to be part of our vibrant community, we have a place for you.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Join Us!</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Connect With Us</h2>\n            <p>Have questions or want to get involved? Reach out!</p>\n            <p>Email: <span class=\"highlight\">info@communityconnect.org</span></p>\n            <p>Phone: <span class=\"highlight\">(123) 456-7890</span></p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Community Connect. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}